reviewText:
I have been looking for this particular VHS tape for the longest. I was on stage that year on this same show. I received this item in new condition and very satisfied with it. Amazon.com always comes through for me and I have never had a problem with my purchases. I'm happy with my purchase and at a very reasonable price as well. I plan on continuing my buying endeavors with Amazon.com sales. Thank you guys,

-George ^_^
